Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:04.84,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT军 直布罗陀基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干这种事 干这种事的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做恶梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰和梅琳 被我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了 真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 那我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你做的恶梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我下手就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太善良了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样什么都保护不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以Heaven's Base战的功绩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,授予真·飞鸟星云勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 这是第二枚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外将这个授予真·飞鸟和雷·查·巴勒路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎么会 没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们信赖你们力量的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请以此为傲 不辜负此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后也要尽心尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不胜光荣 必将尽力做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…不 本人也会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:50.67,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.42,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.67,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,是 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.43,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.34,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到第二枚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的不予置评让人有点胆寒啊 塔利雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让真和雷当上FAITH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本就做好准备被你责问了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但都不是能随便说的 就没提了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想听的话就别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击坠阿斯兰·萨拉和梅琳·霍克的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查明罗德·吉普利尔的所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡潘塔利亚情报部传来的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡潘塔利亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉普利尔去找赛兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且似乎ZAFT也已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,卡潘塔利亚已经有舰队出发前往初岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们要求交出他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Base战他有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而从已知的各种证词看来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的罪状是不可推脱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对其的包庇行为绝对不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡潘塔利亚已有舰队携此要求出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一 我们也要采取非常行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为先头 Minerva立即出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰…现在出发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们若不表明我们是认真的根本无法交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva以速度著称吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连续作战实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但拜托了 库拉提斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布不仅以其高度的军事技术为傲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也拥有Mass Driver这条通天的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.82,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Mass Driver  质量加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很在意那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若吉普利尔掌握了奥布的军力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和月球的联合军会合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT本土也可能再次受到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能忘记他才是Blue Cosmos的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是说奥布会帮助他?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在他就在奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个国家不可能不知道我们在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布是Logos阵营的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的Blue Cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才没回应议长的号召
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布在Junius 7事件之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是作为友国的亲密国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到这点就很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们在这件事上一步也不能退让
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能再容忍Logos在暗地里活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要逮住他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.02,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布领地 初岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不下出击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是都逼到领海前面来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来初岛?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听说是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 政府没有任何表示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像报导也被管制了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要完成所有作业还需要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎 电子系统 补给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各方面加起来 最快也要两天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能尽快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶不上的话就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 在那里瞎忙也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说还不一定会开战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要鲁莽行事 等待乌纳特等人的应对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 奇萨卡上校也是此意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:24.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点脑子的人都看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.54,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布本岛 赛兰官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那狄兰达尔的骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是世界受其支配 你们也没有容身之处了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过不用担心 我们也很快就能反击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要让他回天上我也上天奏起Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想撑到那时候 现在该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聪明的你早该心知肚明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌纳特·艾玛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布政府发出答覆文
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发到扬声器上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我代表奥布政府 答覆通告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰要求引渡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗德·吉普利尔此人不存在于我国内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外 这种武力恫吓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是对我主权国家尊严的侵害行为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深表遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 要求你们立即退兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢如此愚弄我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为这么说我们就不敢打了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种…这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情势下怎么可能被接受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来别无他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我们没心思陪他们演这种闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然以这种虚情假意回应我们的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我凭着正义和对和平的热切期望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誓要与此对抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把罗德·吉普利尔从奥布揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.90,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布近海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.21,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fury 作战计划开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:18.13,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,下令红色状态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认攻击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布本土 赛兰官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国防本部 奥布行政府
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法多姆队ASH 狄路队GOOhN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全机打开武器保险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标虽是罗德·吉普利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对勾结Logos的奥布政府也不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迅速除掉或捕获他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力把平民的损失降低到最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT舰上M.S.出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ASH GOOhN DINN BABI GOUF
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布军呢 怎么部署的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避难情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没动静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没发出避难警报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 初岛海域的事态似乎也未告知民众
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布本土受到轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标似乎是赛兰官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰还不能出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 引擎还没搞定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌M.S.群展开 数量40 正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:47.88,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,初岛 奥布军 国防本部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:47.18,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,曾我上校 敌军正步步逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:49.68,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,为何还未发布任何命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市民的避难也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续呼叫行政府
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛兰在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎么会变这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明说了他不在为什么还打来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为知道是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府为何发布那种愚蠢的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是以前Archangel来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府和情况都和当时不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 总之我们也采取防卫措施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护卫舰群出动 开始迎击 M.S.队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能允许他们继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一第二护卫舰群出动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即驱逐敌军威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.S.队出击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一到第四小队到伊邪那岐海岸防线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿玛基 Murasame队能出动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长  Sky Grasper借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只有我们也得出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太胡闹了 用Sky Grasper
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布正面临再度被战火煎熬的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇萨卡上校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉卡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 阿玛基
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机体先借用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了等不了 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 跟我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样坐视不管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如和国土一起化为焦炭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此会让人很困扰才叫你跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想去当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是先听听乌兹米阁下的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里刻着字吧 读读
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿这扇大门永不会打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这扇门打开的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意味着奥布再次被战火包围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这就是乌兹米阁下被封印的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金黄色的M.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有一天希望得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为答覆我赠与你此物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能传授你的事还有许多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只要你愿意学习
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就必能从爱戴支持你的人们身上学得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我只赠与你此物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量单单是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贪得无厌诚然不可取
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以卵击石亦非明智之举
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守护之剑 现在需要的话拿起它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是为了你认为必须完成的事业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我真心祈愿你永远不会听到我这段话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许对已打开这扇门的你是无法传达的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请幸福地活下去 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐上Akatsuki吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ORB-01  Akatsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系统启动 请出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉·尤拉·阿斯哈 Akatsuki出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新松原第二防线被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本土防线全面崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不重整旗鼓会全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那快干啊 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是在等您的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说这种话 再吃败仗可就全怪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不重整防线的话会全线崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先控制国防本部 重整战线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一号小队跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的去防线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾我上校 海岸上空出现新的友军部队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,识别信号是Takemikazuchi搭载机的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有未知M.S.一台 与Murasame一起朝这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金黄色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是乌兹米·纳拉·阿斯哈之女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉·尤拉·阿斯哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国防本部听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事出突然也许令人怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和指挥官说话 请…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你来啦 我的甜心 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的女神 指挥官是我 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你承认我为奥布联合首长国真正的代表首相卡嘉莉·尤拉·阿斯哈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然当然当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那以此权限下令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将士们立即以叛国罪逮捕拘禁尤拉·罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我奉命拘禁您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从尤拉嘴里打听出吉普利尔的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乌纳特应该是在行政府吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布全军现在开始归入我指挥 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,残存Astray队到孝光方集结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分两小队Murasame掩护上空 保护国土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多兹队中弹 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12区域海岸线 遭到反扑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才明明已经全线崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再派2个小队左右的GOUF过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这国家也该老老实实束手就擒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8点方向 Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离20
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉普利尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还未发现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎抵抗得非常顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用3人出场 我就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打奥布的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也得由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认全系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始出击程序
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闸门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹射器启动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny 请出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真·飞鸟  Destiny出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是本人自愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真以FAITH的权限志愿出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也以相同权限予以认可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请舰长理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐 请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT的援兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉明白的事 卡嘉莉明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这之后真也明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候坚强的自己 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不会放弃梦想 现在力量已经苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.59,0:23:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由与正义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化为一阵狂风吧 Dom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:23.73,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,握った拳の強さで砕けた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:34.33,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,願いに血を流す掌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:44.38,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,果てない翼と鎖は良く似て
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:55.50,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,重さで何処にも行けずに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:05:04.80,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,亡くすばかりの幼い瞳で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:15.32,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,人は還らぬ星を想う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:25.26,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,掲げたそれぞれの火を 命と咲かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:31.03,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,運んで行くことが運命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:45.64,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,輝き刻む 誰もが優しい 刻の傷痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:23.73,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,紧握的双拳粉碎了梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:34.33,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,鲜血染红了双手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:44.38,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的双翼如同枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:55.50,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,沉重得去飞不到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:05:04.80,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡充满了幼小的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:15.32,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,星星承载着失去的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:25.26,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,让生命 像纷纷燃起的火焰般绽放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:31.03,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,命运的转动不会停息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:45.64,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,把人们温柔的光辉 化作时间的伤痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:04:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:06.09,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の姿は僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:15.51,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに泣いてるよに胸に響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.95,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,何も知らないほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:30.70,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,幸せというけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:37.79,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はきっと滿足しないはずだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:44.00,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕が選んだ今を生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.55,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:55.10,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の速さは僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:58.81,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,齒止めのきかなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:02.50,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,空が怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:10.25,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はいつまで頑張ればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:20.16,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,二人ならば終わらせることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:06.09,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:15.51,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,犹如静静的哭泣在心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:26.95,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:30.70,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:37.79,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我却无法满足于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:44.00,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,接受自己选择的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.55,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:55.10,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的速度与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:58.81,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,当一切无法停止时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:02.50,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,开始害怕天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:10.25,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我要奋斗到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:20.16,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的话就会让它结束

